text:
RT @cliffordlevy: Feels like the right time to remind everyone to follow the @nytimes White House team, the best in the business: @peterbakernyt @maggieNYT @anniekarni @shearm @katierogers @michaelcrowley
They ask tough questions of the President.

name: nytimes
text: At least 161 children in New York have gotten sick — and 3 have died — from a mysterious syndrome linked to the coronavirus. A team of more than 30 disease detectives is now racing to learn more. https://t.co/aYHAwVsZNO

name: nytimes
text: RT @ewong: NEW: US officials warn China on proposed security law on Hong Kong. @SecPompeo says it would be a “death knell” — and he signals US may revoke preferential trade status of HK. China benefits from HK as global commerical hub. w/ @michaelcrowley @anaswanson. https://t.co/NCagOGaPME

name: nytimes
text: The video captured by William Bryan brought the world’s attention to the killing of Ahmaud Arbery. Authorities now say Bryan participated in the deadly confrontation. “If we believed he was a witness, we wouldn’t have arrested him," an official said. https://t.co/0pztdRmaLS
